Package: zx48c
Type: Package
Title: Functions for forecasting daily sales
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Shpiruk Dmytro
Maintainer: The package maintainer <shpiruk.d@gmail.com>
Description: The package including functions for forecasting daily demand for e-commerce and retail.
    The forecast functions used short-time history period and calculate coefficients of weekly seasonality. 
    Also it includes two types of sales filtration from unexpected pikes.
